        <p>Some features require a paid subscription. Payments are securely processed through our payment partners. Refunds are handled according to our <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="PrivacyNotice" style="color:#e91e63;text-decoration:none;">Privacy and Refund Policy</a>.</p>
