        <p>Your privacy is important to us. Please read our <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="PrivacyNotice" style="color:#e91e63;text-decoration:none;">Privacy Notice</a> to understand how we handle your personal data.</p>

        <h2>7. Termination</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these Conditions of Use or engage in any harmful activity.</p>

        <h2>8. Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>Dating House provides its services “as is.” We make no guarantees about the accuracy, safety, or outcomes of matches made through the platform.</p>

        <h2>9. Updates to These Conditions</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page, and your continued use signifies your acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

        <div class="footer-note">
            💖 Thank you for being part of the <strong>Dating House</strong> community.
            We’re committed to helping you find meaningful connections safely and respectfully.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>